{
  "stem": "25651.11",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he called his girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in this sort of larking about, he tells her, look, have you got a young girl for these-- two young girls for these two boys?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she says, sure, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know just the girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she comes back with one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then they say, well, she'll have to choose between the two of you which one she likes better, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were not too near each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were like 50 yards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she didn't-- but she said she liked me as a boyfriend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, what sort of boyfriend it is, you know. 50 yards, you can call across the wire.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly the SS man who is in charge of the Kleiderkammer comes around-- not the officer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the ranks of the SS were handling prisoners.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the beating was done by the ranks up to Sergeant, all right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sergeant is scharfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oberscharfuhrer is Sergeant.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then comes officers-- lieutenant, and so on, and sturmbannfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The SS had their own ranks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it wasn't the officer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the scharfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He comes with a stick.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he says, I'm going to punish you for this [GERMAN]-- immoral behavior.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Immoral behavior.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were calling across the wire to girls who were 50 feet away, you know, across the road and across two-- two sets of-- two-- two fences.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he doesn't punish Rudy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because Rudy and him have got a trade relationship, you see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he knows that Rudy has girlfriends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he shuts his eyes to this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The immoral behavior is by these two boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So-- oh, we were allowed to grow our hair by this time, these two boys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The others had their hair shorn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But because we were special prisoners, we were allowed to grow hair.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
